## 📊 Key Business Metrics & SQL Analysis

### 1️⃣ Monthly Recurring Revenue (MRR)

Calculates total revenue per month.

![Monthly Revenue](screenshots/01_monthly_revenue.png)

---

### 2️⃣ Revenue Growth Percentage

Uses CTE + LAG() window function to calculate month-over-month growth.

![Revenue Growth](screenshots/02_revenue_growth.png)

---

### 3️⃣ Customer Lifetime Value (CLTV)

Calculates total revenue generated by each customer.

![CLTV](screenshots/03_cltv.png)

---

### 4️⃣ Top 5 Customers

Uses RANK() window function to identify highest spending customers.

![Top Customers](screenshots/04_top_customers.png)

---

### 5️⃣ Rolling 3-Month Average Revenue

Uses window frame functions to smooth revenue trends.

![Rolling Average](screenshots/05_rolling_avg.png)

